{"tid":957252,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最難忘既聖誕節/除夕倒數","createTime":"2018-12-27T01:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T06:02:05.000Z","uid":41411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4169b4d6a87fd2a3498f366b00f778565e0e1219","tid":957252,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T01:24:21.000Z","msg":"我好簡單 中學果陣成班FD去個同學屋企倒數<br />\n然後女神早走 成班FD都知我鍾意佢 就叫我送女神返屋企<br />\n然後真係送左 果段路程雖然唔長 大概行15分鐘<br />\n但感覺上好似行左成粒鐘 好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到佢屋企樓下仲攬左下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就算有拍拖 但都無依次咁難忘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享下你地既難忘經歷"},{"pid":"6e70ac985b566e87b1570ea20c30fe5eb0d19fd0","tid":957252,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T01:24:51.000Z","msg":"打錯 唔係倒數 而家聖誕party"},{"pid":"56eeb0b5382ef6827bbf257cbaa3935c5f968450","tid":957252,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b4aa46321ef420f243f9286867052f8664f067","tid":957252,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"1月1日0時0分係街成班人係到鳩叫新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家已經準備緊一條友過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db29ccba2056424a19302843c08dd928854ae3b8","tid":957252,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff87535ab0557ad4b78abb27e4d0ce57f3f1d51","tid":957252,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}